        <name>caps</name>
        <qualifiedname>bt_mesh_blob_cli_cb::caps</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Capabilities retrieval completion callback. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called when the capabilities retrieval procedure completes, indicating that a common set of acceptable transfer parameters have been established for the given list of Target nodes. All compatible Target nodes have status code <ref refid="group__bt__mesh__blob_1gga7b5e2895a6577103a8a680a94ee7776daac639c3c82cf48a394c13e3b057c9c0d" kindref="member">BT_MESH_BLOB_SUCCESS</ref>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cli</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>BLOB Transfer Client instance. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>caps</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Safe transfer capabilities if the transfer capabilities of at least one Target node has satisfied the Client, or NULL otherwise. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
        <location file="zephyr/bluetooth/mesh/blob_cli.h" line="202" column="1" bodyfile="zephyr/bluetooth/mesh/blob_cli.h" bodystart="202" bodyend="-1"/>
